    dc:creator "Lorence, David H.; Wagner, Warren L.; Wood, Kenneth R.; Smith, Alan R." ;
    dc:date "2011" ;
    dc:title "New pteridophyte species and combinations from the Marquesas Islands, French Polynesia" ;
